# LLMs/ code loads the project ROOT `.env` (see LLMs/main.py: project_root/.env).
#
# Setup (from repository root):
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Required for Semantic Kernel flows:
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#
# Optional:
#   GOOGLE_API_KEY=...   (if using Gemini / judge features)
